snippet.title: "In Fear I Trust" Opening video
snippet.description: Enjoy the opening for the first episode of In Fear I Trust. Consider it an introduction to an episodic psychological thriller that'll break you like a bad habit; 1979 never looked so nefarious, let alone on the iPad.
